          "description": "My visit to Sky Dental was phenomenal! The office is in a great location and is very nice. Everyone at the front desk was very welcoming and my wait was minimal. The entire staff was very pleasant and I felt that I could have a productive conversation about my dental health with everyone. I feel more confident about my dental health after my conversations with Chris and Dr. Torkian. Scheduling my next visit with Jessie was easy and at any point where someone from the team suggested a treatment I did not feel pressured at all to make a decision. Very happy with my visit and look forward to coming back for my next cleaning!",
